This paper deals with computer vision and robotics, specifically with the problem of object detection and pose estimation. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also uses deep learning techniques, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper mentions applications in navigation and robotics, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.RO (Robotics and Control). Finally, the paper deals with image processing, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.MM (Multimedia).
